```

## Log Levels

| Level        | Meaning                                |
| ------------ | -------------------------------------- |
| **DEBUG**    | Detailed diagnostics (debug mode only) |
| **INFO**     | Important events                       |
| **WARNING**  | Issues recovered from                  |
| **ERROR**    | Failures affecting functionality       |
| **CRITICAL** | System-wide failures                   |

